dataColl.cleanOps:
          Data editing took place at a number of stages throughout the processing, including:
a) Field  form checking;
b) In office during single data entry
c) In office during double data entry
d) Missing checking in CSPro;
e) Range checking in CSPro;
f) Logic checking in CSPro
g) Structure checking in CSPro
h) Secondary editing
Detailed documentation of the editing of data can be found in the "Data processing guidelines" document provided as an external resource.
